                        <h3><a href="/erb">Edge Route Bridge (ERB)</a></h3>
                        <p>The edge-routed bridging overlay performs routing at IRB interfaces located at the edge of the overlay (most often at the leaf devices). As a result, Ethernet bridging and IP routing happen as close to the end systems as possible,
                            but still support Ethernet dependent applications at the end system level.</p>
