                    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8 adj_text">
                        <h3><a href="/crb">Central Route Bridge (CRB)</a></h3>
                        <p>A centrally-routed bridging overlay performs routing at a central location in the EVPN network. In this design, IRB interfaces are configured in the overlay at each spine device to route traffic between the VLANs that originate
                            at the leaf devices and end systems. For an overview of centrally-routed bridging overlays, see the Centrally-Routed Bridging Overlay section in Data Center Fabric Blueprint Architecture Components.</p>
                        <div class="readtext">
