                        </div>
                        <h3><a href="/collapsed-spine">Collapsed Spine</a></h3>
                        <p>In collapsed spine fabrics, core EVPN-VXLAN overlay functions are collapsed only onto a spine layer. There is no leaf layer; the spine devices can interface directly to existing top-of-rack (ToR) switches in the access layer that
                            might not support EVPN-VXLAN.</p>
                        <div class="readtext">
                            <a href="/collapsed-spine">Click here</a> to begin building an CRB configuration
